{"tid":880583,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊幾年都無剛需","createTime":"2018-10-28T20:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T06:22:22.000Z","uid":28068,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7e5899362d38a2e41504bb87244861d5076ae6","tid":880583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T20:39:25.000Z","msg":"因為近五年供應量根本就大過需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5至10年前香港就真係有剛需<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為個幾年私樓推出既單位數每年得幾千個至10000個多d<br />\n公屋又得幾千個至10000個<br />\n加埋都係僅僅夠每年既新家庭住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且樓價一路升<br />\n所以個時有錢既都買多一兩層黎炒 加幾按槓桿再炒<br />\n或者幫仔女俾定首期供住先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但黎緊5至十年<br />\n私數每年數估計有差唔多15000－20000個單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n居屋又重新推出<br />\n公+私接近有40000單位<br />\n未來5年每年新家庭數目頂多咪得30000<br />\n都會少過供應量成幾千個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未來一年幾千個單位搵邊個硬食？<br />\n香港空置率已經高到要收稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊幾年d空置單位如果放係同一區香港一樣有鬼城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算真係有剛需都鬥唔嬴剛供<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習主席都有講 樓係用黎住 唔係用黎炒<br />\n政府明顯就係要打壓樓價<br />\n唔爆先奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6d10c88158c3033fe058f6b13cb7e95fa3aa0d","tid":880583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T20:55:17.000Z","msg":"兩句講晒<br />\n樓市呢十幾年一路升係有剛需<br />\n黎緊5年跌就係剛供累事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怪就怪地產商呢幾年係咁起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f154a037aad4f1bd0d0ce29b76180150a3d6a4","tid":880583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"香港統計月刊<br />\n至 2051 年的香港家庭住戶推算<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71710FC2017XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB71710FC2017XXXXB0100.pdf&d=ovH9S1ofknESdWIPPMJb854f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2cc35435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71710FC2017XXXXB0100.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來黎緊10年  每年得29000個新家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日150都越黎越少<br />\n每年多左10000個單位點接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d92cc6a11ee6b5103dd316a5c73500daaa783bd","tid":880583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T21:28:46.000Z","msg":"黎緊五年<br />\n每年有5000個居屋單位<br />\n淨係居屋＋私樓都搞掂住宅需求<br />\n仲未計綠置居<br />\n<br />\n公屋輪候冊好快會低過25萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b6ab1512d6fbde6cade35c480dbd0531ef9cc3","tid":880583,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T22:35:35.000Z","msg":"你計漏一點<br />\n移民數字一年高過一年<br />\n唔好講話佢地走咗需求少咗啲咁表面嘅野<br />\n佢地為走佬手上嘅物業都要放，唔係點攞錢走，德福有版你睇，賤價求走"},{"pid":"e6e80c680c103e378fdbdc2b85c36b46fadb185b","tid":880583,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T22:52:30.000Z","msg":"跌未呀咁"},{"pid":"38fcb3d4a91a1344c77efad1e1efd34f04eafcb7","tid":880583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08b6ab1512d6fbde6cade35c480dbd0531ef9cc3","tid":880583,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T22:35:35.000Z","msg":"你計漏一點<br />\n移民數字一年高過一年<br />\n唔好講話佢地走咗需求少咗啲咁表面嘅野<br />\n佢地為走佬手上嘅物業都要放，唔係點攞錢走，德福有版你睇，賤價求走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"其實計多俾佢<br />\n因為唔係每個新家庭都買樓<br />\n跌市一定好多選擇租"},{"pid":"8645839305575d15cddc1b91f0cf66a4f94f0275","tid":880583,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"一陣個閪政府話<br />\n由於樓宇買賣市場慘<br />\n宣布150增加至300人<br />\n舒緩樓市 剛需gogogo"},{"pid":"8755fd306505ac61563aaac4645e26b7fbd492b9","tid":880583,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8645839305575d15cddc1b91f0cf66a4f94f0275","tid":880583,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"一陣個閪政府話<br />\n由於樓宇買賣市場慘<br />\n宣布150增加至300人<br />\n舒緩樓市 剛需gogogo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"屍苦<br />\n有錢買果啲先叫肛衰<br />\n係地產鋪門口望住啲價錢係咁打飛機<br />\n唔叫肚衰囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca786c344a2c2a0781bfeb61a81b4f9edf41eccc","tid":880583,"uid":84771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0f154a037aad4f1bd0d0ce29b76180150a3d6a4","tid":880583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"香港統計月刊<br />\n至 2051 年的香港家庭住戶推算<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71710FC2017XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB71710FC2017XXXXB0100.pdf&d=ovH9S1ofknESdWIPPMJb854f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2cc35435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B71710FC2017XXXXB0100.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來黎緊10年  每年得29000個新家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日150都越黎越少<br />\n每年多左10000個單位點接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"10年290000萬個新家庭，都幾大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}